title: 69 Timothy Sykes: Creating the Next Outrageous Millionaire Lifestyle
description:
If you could source a millionaire to work day and night in to get you to your goal of a million dollars, would you follow them?
Our next guest on the School of Greatness turned $12,415 in $3.93 million in less than 3 years. His story is amazing.
To see videos, get show notes and connect with the School, please visit lewishowes.com/69
author: podcast@schoolofgreatness.com (Lewis Howes)
